dc_title_s: Registered Rental Properties: Franklin County, Ohio
dc_description_s: Franklin County Auditor - Local Government Information Model - Assessment Information - Registered Rental Properties This point layer contains properties that are registered with the Auditor's office as rental properties. This is not an exhaustive list of rental properties, it is however all properties that are have an active rental registration on file with the Auditor's office. This layer is regenerated on nightly based on the previous days transactions. The parcel centroid values are utilized to create these points with condominium units being spatially accurate. This layer follows ERSI's Local Government Information Model (LGIM) schema and has been edited to meet the needs of the Franklin County Auditor and our customers.
